data.title: Lais Ribeiro Lounges at Home for M Magazine Milenio
data.meta_description: Lais Ribeiro is ready for her closeup on M Magazine Milenio's latest cover. Photographed by Silja Magg, the Brazilian beauty wears a green Givenchy parka.
data.text:
Photos by Silja Magg

Styling by Sarah Gore Reeves

Lais Ribeiro is ready for her closeup on M Magazine Milenio’s latest cover. Photographed by Silja Magg, the Brazilian beauty wears a green Givenchy parka. 2020 also marks ten years of Lais’ modeling career, and we can see why with her natural beauty. Sarah Gore Reeves styled her over FaceTime with casual-chic looks. She models pieces from labels such as Nike, Victoria’s Secret, and Maison Margiela.
